  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four people were injured in the bus accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A private bus traveling from Nuwara Eliya area towards Labukalai area has gone off the road in Nuwaraeliya-Kandy main road at Labukalai sub-division and crashed.",
        "The bus was carrying passengers from Nuwara Eliya area yesterday (14) evening",
        "More than 30 people were traveling in the bus and during the accident, only 4 people were injured.",
        "Direct investigations revealed that the accident happened because the driver could not control the speed of the bus.",
        "All the 4 people injured in the accident have been admitted to the Nuwara Eliya District Hospital and are undergoing treatment there."
      ],
